deploy to a container
# cd /opt/tomcat/webapps/manager/META-INF
#nano context.xml
comment the valve attribute
in the Jenkins page -> manage jenkins->plugins->available plugins->install deploy to container
now navigate to manage jenkins->credentails->system->global credentails=>add creadentail=>
			set username=>tomcatscript
			password=>tomcatscriptpwd
			id =>tomcatscript
			description=>credentials to connect to tomcat
create a new job 
goals and options==>clean install
navigate to deploy to container=>add postbuild action=>deploy war/ear files=>
				war/ear=>target/helloworld.war
				contextpath=>/helloworld
				add tomcatcontainer
